					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3088877#post-3713423</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3088877/scp-3049#post-3713423</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2018 19:07:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ObserverSeptember</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1488791</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zSgiXGELjbc&amp;ab_channel=melodysheep">A still more glorious dawn awaits/not a sunrise, but a galaxy rise/a morning filled with 400 billion suns/the rising of the Milky Way</a></em></p> <p>My only complaint is the line directly referencing <em>Cosmos</em> is too on the nose. Aside from that, this is a simple idea executed brilliantly. I completely got the message you were going for, the symbolism of the apple pie, and the reason the Doctor was so disturbed by what she saw.</p> <p>A wonderful reminder of our own cosmic insignificance. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
