						 <p>I don't like it. The idea overall is too on-the-nose, and the interview is just cringeworthy old people jokes and bad dialogue.</p> <p>The only thing keeping me from downvoting is that the universe itself is turned into an apple pie. I mean, that's unexpected, but literally nothing else about this is.</p> 
