								<wikidot:authorUserId>2826145</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Brilliant! I love &quot;contained-universe&quot; SCPs, and this is a fantastic example of one. The ending is particularly horrific; the entire universe, development of the civilisation, technological advancement &amp;c are just put in place to create a pie. And the agent eating the pie without realising what he is doing&#8230; absolutely fantastic. An easy +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
