					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Why do people that know how this skip works have to receive evaluations and amnestics?</p> </blockquote> <p>Because they caused the deaths of untold numbers of sophonts (but probably in the order of nonillions) in order to get a fucking pie. Genocide on a scale that is literally inconceivable for most people just for a common pastry. Presumably the Foundation is worried about moral wounds.</p> 
