					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3088877#post-3487066</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3088877/scp-3049#post-3487066</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 21 Jul 2017 16:00:03 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>rioludoodle</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3165531</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><em>&quot;To make an apple pie from scratch, you must first create the universe.&quot; &#8212; Carl Sagan.</em></p> <p>This SCP was inspired by my love of Carl Sagan quotes and <em>Rick and Morty</em>'s disturbing cartoon insanity as seen in the Microverse Battery episode.</p> <p>Thank you to darkgreeny, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leveritas" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1558990&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="Leveritas" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1558990)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leveritas" >Leveritas</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rigen" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2826105&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="Rigen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2826105)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rigen" >Rigen</a></span> for their feedback. <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" >sirpudding</a></span>, while I wish you would have said a little more about the draft, it was and always will be fun to hear about the eventual heat death of the expanding universe. :)</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Translations</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Translations</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3049">SCP-3049 in Chinese</a>, translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thomasx" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2789139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="ThomasX" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2789139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thomasx" >ThomasX</a></span></li> <li><a href="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/scp-3049">SCP-3049 in Japanese</a>, translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-dives" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2375337&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="C-Dives" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2375337)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-dives" >C-Dives</a></span></li> <li><a href="http://ko.scp-wiki.net/scp-3049">SCP-3049 in Korean</a>, translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mgpedersen" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1774469&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="MGPedersen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1774469)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mgpedersen" >MGPedersen</a></span></li> <li><a href="http://lafundacionscp.wikidot.com/scp-3049">SCP-3049 in Spanish</a>, translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/morhadow" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3535580&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="morhadow" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3535580)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/morhadow" >morhadow</a></span></li> <li><a href="http://fondationscp.wikidot.com/scp-3049">SCP-3049 in French</a>, translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karnot" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3784006&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="Karnot" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3784006)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karnot" >Karnot</a></span></li> <li><a href="http://scpfoundation.net/scp-3049">SCP-3049 in Russian</a>, translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/man1990" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5515896&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572140796" alt="Man1990" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5515896)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/man1990" >Man1990</a></span></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Image&nbsp;credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Image&nbsp;credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li><a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/70684282@N00/6014911331">Stove/oven</a> image belongs to &quot;bats22&quot; on Flickr under the <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/">CC BY 2.0</a> license. Image was modified by me using Paint Tool SAI and a public domain image belonging to NASA.</li> <li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Apple_pie_fresh_out_of_the_oven.jpg">Pie</a> image belongs to &quot;Sage Ross&quot; on Wikimedia Commons under the <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.en">CC BY-SA 3.0</a> license.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> 
